[l] Es gibt jetzt fuer Transgender-Frauen eine Behandlung, um selbst Kinder stillen zu koennen.The three-and-a-half month treatment involved the use of hormones, a nausea drug, and a breast pump to stimulate milk production. The mother was able to produce about 8 ounces (227 grams) of milk a day, which is below average but enough to sustain a newborn. She was able to exclusively breastfeed her baby for six weeks, after which time she supplemented with formula.
